data.description: Motivated seller! Well maintained home, move right in. Owners bedroom is on the first floor with adjoining bathroom. New Kitchen Flooring and paint. Enjoy the spacious fenced in backyard detached garage that has electric. The bedroom on second floor has an extra space around 11 x 13. Measurements are approximate. Pre-Approval before showing.  Due to Perchwell errors the Roof is Shingle, home has Vinyl Siding and Vinyl Windows.
